  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1554593">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1554593/" class="title-link">建议真的要看的话，买英译本吧，法语我不懂</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1554593"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3132248/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3132248-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3132248/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">元元</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar10 main-title-rating" title="很差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-11-13"
      class="main-meta">2008-11-13 21:32:52</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1554593_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  就当译者使用了金山快译，我不知道10年是什么概念，但是肯定不会有一句中文句子超过30个字，还没有标点符号。语法习惯更是照抄原文，定语、状语后置这类普通中文里不太会出现的句式比比皆是。  苦啊，要读一本好书也不是容易的事

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1554593/#comments">(14回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 8没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
